	 <title>System.IsLetter</title> 
	 <para></para> 
	 <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Remarks</bridgehead> 
	 <para>If AIndex is specified, <symbol>IsLetter</symbol> returns
		  <symbol>true</symbol> if the character AString[AIndex] is a letter, otherwise
		  <symbol>IsLetter</symbol> returns <symbol>false</symbol>.</para> 
	 <para> If AIndex is not specified, <symbol>IsLetter</symbol> returns
		  <symbol>true</symbol> if every character of AString is a letter, otherwise
		  <symbol>IsLetter</symbol> returns <symbol>false</symbol>. 
		  <note> 
				<para>Dataphor uses zero based indexing.</para> 
		  </note></para> 
	 <example> 
		  <title>Example</title> 
		  <programlisting>select IsLetter("123abc");
select IsLetter("123abc", 4);</programlisting> 
		  <programlisting>False
True</programlisting> 
	 </example> 
